{
  "stem": "21319.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If she can't see him, she was crying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because she was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She had a baby in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she can't see her husband.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She can't do this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they threw her out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what I want to say, in the beginning, the Poles cooperated very much with the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And wait and see, when somebody of the Poles read this story.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they will say no, this never happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She's lying.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How did things changed for you now, with the German invasion?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, I lost everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I lost my husband.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I lost my brother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I lost my sisters.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Half of my family was already killed, for the first few months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they pushed us in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And i was in the ghetto with my baby and my mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then my mother was taken, went to the other ghetto, the smaller ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But then-- but then-- mine's brother-in-law, the other one, from my sister, Rivka, they-- there was a factory for fur.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They gathered all the furs from the Jewish woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they remade them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they send it to their wives in Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they needed slave work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they grabbed all the Jews up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Like, they made, like, a little ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this were on the outskirts of town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's where my sister, Rivka, was with her children, two boys and her husband.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my sister, Chasia, was for-- with-- she had a baby in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she-- and then my mother went with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because I was-- they moved me from one block in the ghetto to the other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they-- and they probably was planning, at that time, to wipe out the ghetto completely.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So my mother went with them, there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
